walkthrough.initialSetup.title: Setup dbt Power User
walkthrough.initialSetup.description: Setup the dbt Power User extension for your project by following the steps shown below.
walkthrough.initialSetup.steps.support.t: Welcome to dbt Power User setup!
walkthrough.initialSetup.steps.support.d: Before you begin, know that our team is on standby to assist you. Should you encounter any issues or have questions, [contact us](https://www.altimate.ai/support) right away.
walkthrough.initialSetup.steps.open.desc:
To start off, open a dbt project.
[Open dbt Project](command:toSide:vscode.openFolder)
walkthrough.initialSetup.steps.selectInt:
Choose the Python Interpreter where you have installed dbt.
[Select Python Interpreter](command:python.setInterpreter)
walkthrough.initialSetup.steps.installDb:
Please install dbt in the selected Python Environment.
[Install dbt](command:dbtPowerUser.installDbt)
walkthrough.initialSetup.steps.updateExt:
To get the latest features, update the dbt Power User extension.
[Update Extension](command:workbench.extensions.action.extensionUpdates)
walkthrough.initialSetup.steps.associate:
For dbt Power User to work, *.sql file types need to be associated with the value 'sql' or 'jinja-sql' and *.yml file types should be associated with the value 'yaml' or 'jinja-yaml'.
[Associate File Types](command:toSide:dbtPowerUser.associateFileExts)
walkthrough.initialSetup.steps.validateP:
Check if the dbt project is setup correctly. This will run dbt debug to ensure that dbt is able to locate the profile and connect to the database. You can validate multiple projects one by one as well
[Validate Project](command:dbtPowerUser.validateProject)

Check if the dbt project is setup correctly. This will run dbt environment show to ensure that dbt is able to locate the profile and connect to the database. You can validate multiple projects one by one as well
[Validate Project](command:dbtPowerUser.validateProject)
walkthrough.initialSetup.steps.pickProje:
Now, letâ€™s validate the dbt project that you are working on by checking for dbt dependencies and identifying any issues in the configuration.
[Pick Project](command:dbtPowerUser.pickProject)
walkthrough.initialSetup.steps.installDe:
This step will run dbt deps and install or update any packages involved in the project. You should see the results in a terminal that opens up. Each package should say 'Up to Date' as they are installed/ updated.
[Run dbt deps](command:dbtPowerUser.installDeps)
walkthrough.initialSetup.steps.finish.de:
If you followed all the steps so far, the extension should be set up for your project.
If you work with multiple projects in a single workspace, please pick another project and run the steps to install packages and run validation for all of them.
If you still have issues, you can [contact us](https://www.altimate.ai/support) for further help
